<small>you think everything is cool shit.

and BAM! you're life is a mess.

and i love how i'm always the last person to find out everything.

i'm just blah.
maybe i'll lay down.
rummage through my thoughts and see where it gets me. 
i guess its hard when everything is so cluttered.
sometimes i dont know where to start.
and i dont know where i left off.

later.
Shane.

So I gave in! What can I say. She's a powerful young woman. RAWR. LOL. I dont have much to say about myself. But I'm thinking about getting another tattoo. I've got my TV on mute. And its the GRILLZ song. HAHAHA. Its great to just watch the videos on mute. My AIM is DrumThis86 IM me sometime, I'm always up for a good chat. If I'm on. Well tonight I'm going out with a few of my friends. And we'll see what happens. Catch You Later. Shane.
